{"lastModified":1775133496921,"uri":"c::10120242293::vessel::27c293b0-f005-11ee-a725-1dbe0af55ad7","yachtType":["Sailing","Catamaran"],"description":"Operating Area: Croatia\n\nEnjoy the luxury of space, escape the everyday, and connect with nature. With its innovative layout, this catamaran offers durable solutions to preserve the environment and to protect your dream destinations.\n\nThis catamaran has been created for you to make long crossings in exceptional comfort. Relax on the flybridge, with its innovative, modular layout and clever ergonomic design, and enjoy the view: your dream of travel to far-off destinations is finally coming true. Lagoon 51 reveals unique aft transoms, ensuring easy, safe movement on board. Together with the swim platform, this space becomes a true balcony on the water while cruising, and at anchor, an invitation to swim.\n\nWith a bright and inviting interior, numerous on-deck places to relax or socialize, good sailing manners, and a layout ideal for chartering, the Lagoon 51 does several things right. Our Lavina offers 6 cabins for guest, 4 of them are with double semi-island berth with plenty of space for storage and large windows allowing you to enjoy captivating surrounding from the intimacy of your bed. Each of those cabins come with ensuite bathroom, with separated shower area. Front cabins share their bathrooms with cabins situated in the mid ship area through separate entrance door accessible from the halls.\n\nAmid-ship cabins have slightly smaller berth, so ideal for children, or to be used as a single berth for an adult. Also, a good solution for an additional crew member in case you want to add free-lance chef to cater your gastronomic needs during your cruise. Lavina will prove you her abilities to cover wide range of different activities on board in a comfort and a style.","blueprint":{"name":"LAVINA","images":["/media/media::image::a::vessel::27c293b0-f005-11ee-a725-1dbe0af55ad7::assets::dde3f850-fdce-11ef-a2c3-89ff965